---
title: Pork Teriyaki with Egg Noodles, Asparagus, and Sesame
description: Never buy bottled teriyaki sauce again! The flavors of ginger, garlic, soy, and honey make for a much better (and healthier) alternative. Fresh egg noodles cook up quickly and give take-out noodles a serious run for their money.
